:H2.OPEN
:XMP.
Format&gml. &gml.OPEN.opening salutation
              <basic document elements>
:eXMP.
:I2 refid='gtopen'.gtopen
:P.
The :HP2.&gml.open:eHP2. tag specifies the opening salutation text
and must be specified.
The salutation text is placed in the output document followed by
a layout-determined delimiter (such as a colon).
The body of the letter follows the open tag.
The tags :HP2.&gml.attn:eHP2., :HP2.&gml.open:eHP2., and
:HP2.&gml.subject:eHP2. may be specified in any order.
